{
  "stem": "9091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were in very poor condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he agreed to take us back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we were in such poor condition-- mainly me-- that when I reached that Polish orphanage-- I was, as I said, nine years old-- I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to carry me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- my legs and hands were so thin that they gave me a nickname, which stayed to me all during the years till I reached Israel-- Palestine.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the nickname was [POLISH], which means a match, in Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that-- that is how-- how skinny I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, so we reached that-- we were accepted to that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At least we had a place where to sleep and to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we made a point-- I told my brother, OK, each one got a-- a little piece-- in the morning, a little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said-- and something to drink-- so I said to my brother, OK, we'll-- we'll eat both together one piece.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We'll share one piece.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one piece we'll-- we'll-- we'll bring out-- we'll give our mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because she used to come every day, in the morning, to visit us at the gate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So one piece of bread we used to give her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then she disappeared for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Turned out that she went to another place where to stay, because she didn't have where to stay.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she didn't have what to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she went to a kind of another [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It so happened that in that other [NON-ENGLISH], a dog bit her very-- very badly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they had to bring her back to Samarkand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she was put in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
